olive oil
1 packet chicken breast strips
1 packet diced bacon
1 cucumber
1 tomato
1 bag salad leaves
1 bottle Balsamic & Olive Oil Dressing
1 packet garlic aioli
1 sachet Aussie Spice Blend
1 packet Roasted Pumpkin

• In a bowl, combine chicken and spice blend with a drizzle of olive oil
• Heat olive oil in a frying pan over medium-high heat
• Cook chicken and bacon, breaking up bacon with a spoon until browned, 6-8 mins.

• Prick a few holes in pumpkin packet. Microwave until steaming, 3 mins
• Meanwhile, roughly chop cucumber and tomato.

• In a second bowl, combine cucumber, tomato, rocket mix, pumpkin and dressing. Season to taste
• Plate up salad. Top with chicken and bacon
• Serve with aioli